# Project Rules for P2MFashionDesignAccelerator

- **Model Version Constraint**: NEVER use any Gemini model version below 3.1 (e.g., gemini-1.5, gemini-2.0, gemini-2.5) for text, image, or video generation tasks. Always default to and utilize Gemini 3.1 models or newer (e.g., gemini-3.1-flash-lite-preview, gemini-3.1-pro-preview, gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview, veo-3.1-fast-generate-001).
